            <title>[HBASE-2711] allow hbase shell command to operate on group of tables</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2711</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Suppose I have the following 20 tables in HBase:&lt;br/&gt;
ERRORS-1276213362068-1&lt;br/&gt;
ERRORS-1276213362068-2&lt;br/&gt;
ERRORS-1276213362068-3&lt;br/&gt;
...&lt;br/&gt;
ERRORS-1276213362068-20&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;HBase shell commands, such as disable and drop, should be able to operate on group of tables which are identified by prefix or suffix.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
